info.description:
Welcome to gauges-python's documentation!
=========================================

gauges-python that gives you easy access to the Gaug.es API.



.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/Lispython/gauges-python.png
	   :target: https://travis-ci.org/Lispython/gauges-python

Features
--------



INSTALLATION
------------

To use gauges-python  use pip or easy_install:

``pip install gauges``

or

``easy_install gauges``


USAGE
-----



CONTRIBUTE
----------

Fork https://github.com/Lispython/gauges/ , create commit and pull request.
